hadiths[155]{hadithnumber,text}:
3416,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke maine ehale suffa ke kuch afrad ko Quran padhaya aur likhna sikhaya . to un mein se eik shakhs ne mujhey eik qaus (kamaan) hadiyatan di. maine ( dil mein) kaha : ye koi aham maal bhi nahin hai aur main jihad mein iskey zariey se teer andazi hi kar sakta hun, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jata hun aur iskey mutalliq poochhta hun. chunanche main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey eik aadmi ne eik kamaan hadiya ki hai jisey maine likhna sikhaya aur Quran padhaya hai. aur ye koi aham maal bhi nahin, mein uskey zariey se jihad mein teer andazi hi kar sakta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhen ye pasand ho ke tumhen aag ka toq pehnaya jaey, to usey qubul kar lo.''"
3417,"Janab Junaada bin abi Umayya (Rahimahullah) ne , Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se is hadees ki manind riwayat kiya aur pehli riwayat ziyada kamil hai. maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! uski baabat aap ki kya raey hai? to aapney farmaya : ''ye angaara hai jisey to ne apney kandhon ke darmiyan dal liya hai.''"
3418,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik jamaat safar mein gaee . unhoney eik arab qabeela ke yahan padaaw kiya aur un se ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi) talab ki . magar unhoney inkar kar diya. phir aisey hua ke us qabiley ke sardar ko) bichho waghaira ne ( dank maar diya. unhoney uska har tarah se ilaj kiya, magar usey koi faeyda na hua . to un mein se kisi ne kaha : agar tum un logon ke paas jao jo tumharey yahan padaaw kiye huey hain, shayad un mein kisi ke paas koi cheez ho jo tumharey aadmi ke liye mufeed ho. ( to baaz (kuchh) aadmi aaye (aur kaha ke hamarey sardar ko bichho waghaira ne dank maar diya hai aur ham ne uska har tarah se ilaj muaalija kiya hai magar usey fayda nahin hua . to kya tum mein se kisi ke paas koi cheez hai jo hamarey aadmi ke liye mufeed ho? unka maqsad dam tha. Sahaba mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : main dam karta hun. lekin ham ne tum se ziyaafat talab ki thi jis ka tum ne inkar kar diya, to main us waqt tak dam nahin karunga jab tak tum koi iwaz (badal) na do . chunanche unhoney bakriyon ka eik rewad dena tey kiya. phir wo sahabi uskey paas gaey aur us par sura Fatiha padhi . wo us dauran mein us par (halka halka) luaab bhi phoonktey jatey they yahan tak ke wo theek ho gaya goya ke kisi bandhan se khul gaya ho. to unhoney jo moawza tey kiya tha wo dey diya (bakriyan hawaley kar den). sathiyon ne kaha ke unhen aapas mein taqseem kar lein, to jisney dam kiya tha usney kaha : aisey mat karo yahan tak ke pehley ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaeyn aur aap se mashwara karen. chunanche wo subah ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas pahunchey aur aap ko ye qissa bayan kiya to aapney farmaya : ''tumhen kahan se khabar hui thi ke ye dam bhi hai? tum ne bahut khoob kiya. mera bhi is mein hissey rakho.''"
3419,"Ma'bad bin Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees riwayat ki."
3420,"Janab Khaarija bin Salat ne apney chacha ( Hazrat Ilaaqa bin Sihaar Tameemi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kiya ke wo eik qom ke paas se guzrey to wo log unke paas aaye aur kaha : tum us shakhs (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ke paas se khair (Quran aur zikre-Allah) lekar aaye ho, chunanche hamarey us shakhs par dam kar do. phir wo log unke paas eik majnun (deewaney) ko laye jo zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua tha. unhoney usey teen din tak subah shaam sura Fatiha ka dam kiya, wo jab bhi isey khatam kartey to apna luaab jama kartey aur us par phunk detey . phir wo aisey ho gaya jaisey ke bandhan se khol diya gaya ho. un logon ne unko kuchh diya to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur ye sab bayan kiya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kha lo, qasam meri umr ki ! log batil jhaad phunk se khatey hain aur tum ne haq, sach dam se khaya hai.''"
3421,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''seengi laganey waley ki kamai naa-pasandida hai, kuttey ki qeemat khabees (gandi) hai aur bad-kar aurat ki kharchi khabees hai.''"
3422,"Janab ibne Mahisa (Haram bin Saad bin Muhayisa) apney walid (yani dada ( se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney (Muhayisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se pachhney laganey ki ujrat ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, to aapney unhen mana farma diya. wo phir bhi aap se sawal kartey aur ijazat chahtey rahey yahan tak ke aapney unhen hukm diya ke usey apni oontni aur apney ghulam ko khila dey ."
3423,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pachhney lagwaaey aur hajjaam ko uski ujrat di. agar ye kaam ya ujrat khabees (haram) hoti to usey na detey .
3424,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Janab Abu-Taiba ( Naafe ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pachhney lagaey to aapney usey eik saa khajoor deney ka hukm diya. aur uskey malikon se sifarish farmaee ke us par laagoo khiraaj mein kami karen.
3425,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne laundiyon ki kamai se mana farmaya hai.
3426,"Janab Tariq bin Abdur-Rehman Qarshi ne bayan kiya ke Janab Raafe bin Rifaa (Raziallahu anhu) Ansariyon ki eik majlis mein aaye aur kaha ke aaj Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein mana farmaya hai aur kaee chizen zikr kin aur un mein se eik ye thi ke aapney hamein londi ki kamai se mana farmaya hai siwaye iskey jo uskey haath ki kamai ho. aur apni ungliyon se ishara kartey huey kaha ke maslan roti pakaey, oon kaate ya dhunke."
3427,Janab Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne londi ki kamai se mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke jaana jaey ke kahan se kamaya hai.
3428,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat , bad-kar aurat ki kamai aur kaahin ke nazraney se mana farmaya hai."
3429,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne janwar ko jufti karaney ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai.
3430,"Janab Abu-Majida kehtey hain ke maine eik ladkey ka kaan kaat liya . ya merey kaan se kuchh kaat liya gaya to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hajj kartey huey hamarey yahan aaye . ham unke yahan jama ho gaey, to unhoney hamein Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf bhej diya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bila-shuba is mein qisaas hai, hajjaam ko bulao jo us se qisaas ley . jab hajjaam ko bulaya gaya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, farmatey they : ''maine apni khaala ko eik ghulam hiba kiya hai, umeed hai ke wo uskey liye ba-barkat Sabit hoga , aur maine un se kaha hai ke usey kisi hajjaam , sunaar ya qassaab ke hawaley na karna.Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abdul-A'alaa ne ibne Is-haq se riwayat mein kaha ''ibne Maajida , bano Saham ka fard tha aur usney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya."
3431,"Abu-Majida (ibne Maajida) Sehmi ne ba-waaste Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi hadees ki manind riwayat kiya."
3432,"Ibne Maajida Sehmi ne ba-waaste Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki misl (jaisi) riwayat ki."
3433,Hazrat Salim (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney koi ghulam bechaa aur uskey paas maal bhi ho to ye maal uskey farokht kerney waley ka hoga siwaey iske ke kharidar shart kar ley . aur jisney taabeer shuda khajoor bechi to uska phal bechney waley ka hoga siwaey iske ke kharidar shart kar ley.''
3434,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ghulam ka qissa aur Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khajoor ka masla bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Zohri aur Naafe ne chaar hadison mein ikhtilaf kiya hai. un mein se eik ye hai.
3435,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney ghulam farokht kiya aur uskey paas maal ho to uska maal farokht kerney waley ka hoga siwaye iskey ke kharidar shart kar ley.''"
3436,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke saudey par sauda na karey aur na saaman laney walon se raastey mein milo yahan tak ke usey mandi mein utaar liya jaey.''"
3437,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke mandi mein saman laney walon se raastey hi mein mulaqat ki jaey. (yani saman kharida liya jaey) agar koi kharidar us se mila ho aur saman kharida ho to maal waley ko baazar mein aaney ke baad ikhtiyar hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha, Sufiyan (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : koi shakhs kisi ke saudey par sauda na karey yani yun kahey ke merey paas is se das guna behtar hai. (aisa kehna jayez nahin.)"
3438,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saudey par dhoka deney ke liye eik doosrey se badh kar qeemat na lagao.''"
3439,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke koi shahri kisi dehati ke liye kharid aur farokht ka kaam karey. (Taaoos kehtey hain :) maine wazahat chahi ke iska kya mafhoom hai? to kaha ke koi shahri kisi dehati ke liye dalaal na baney ."
3440,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shahri kisi dehati ke liye kharid aur farokht na karey agar-che wo uska bhai ya baap hi kyon na ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Hafs bin umr se suna, unhoney kaha : hamein Abu-Hilaal ne bayan kiya, unhoney kaha : ham se Muhammad (ibne Sirin) Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they ke (lلا يبيع حاضر لباد) ka kalma Jaame maani rakhta hai. yani shahri, dehati ke liye koi cheez bechey , na koi cheez khareedey."
3441,Janab Salim makki se riwayat hai ke eik Erab (dehati) ne un se bayan kiya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main apni eik doodh wali oontni laya aur Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan thehra (aur chaha ke Talha usey farokht kar den) to Talha ne kaha : beshak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke koi shahri kisi dehati ke liye farokht karey. lekin tum khud baazar jao aur dekho ke kon tum se khareednaa chahta hai. phir mujh se mashwara kar lena yahan tak ke main tumhen bata dunga ke tum ne us se sauda karna hai ya nahin.
3442,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shahri kisi dehati ke liye kharid aur farokht na karey. logon ko chhod do , Allah baaz (kuchh) ko baaz se rizq deta hai.''"
3443,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (mandi mein pahunchney se pehley) kharidari ke liye qafilon se mat milo . aur koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke saudey par sauda na karey aur oontni ya bakri ka doodh mat roko . jisney us qism ka janwar kharid liya ho, to doodh doh leney ke baad usey do baaton ka ikhtiyar hai, agar wo pasand ho to rakh ley aur agar pasand na aaye to usey lauta dey aur sath eik saa khajoor bhi dey.''"
3444,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney koi aisi bakri kharid li jis ka doodh roka gaya tha, to usey teen din tak ikhtiyar hai agar wo chahey to wapis kar dey aur eik saa tuaam (khana) bhi sath lautaye , lekin سمراء (umda gehun) na ho.''"
3445,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney koi aisi bakri kharid li jis ka doodh roka gaya tha, phir usey dohaa to agar pasand ho to rakh ley warna (wapis kar dey aur) uskey doodh ke badley eik saa khajoor (malik ko dena) hai.''"
3446,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney koi aisa janwar kharida jis ka doodh roka gaya tha, to usey teen din tak ikhtiyar hai. agar usey wapis karey to uskey doodh ke ba-qadr ya us se dugney gehun bhi wapis karey.''"
3447,"Hazrat Maamer bin Abi Maamer (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur ye bano Adi bin Kab ke fard hain, ye kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi nafarman aur gunahgaar aadmi hi zakhira andozi kar sakta hai.'' (Muhammad bin Amr ne) kaha : maine Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se kaha ke aap bhi to zakhira kartey hain. unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Maamer (Raziallahu anhu) bhi zakhira kiya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) se puchha ke (حكرہ) (zakhira andozi) kya hai? to unhoney farmaya ke wo chizen jin par logon ki guzraan ho (unka zakhira karna mana hai). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Auzaai (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke zakhira andoz wo hota hai jo baazar aata jata rahey. (baazar par nazar rakhey aur aham chizen kharid kar rok ley.)"
3448,"Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke khajoor mein zakhira andozi (rok rakhna jayez) nahin hai. ibne Musanna ne Hasan Basri se bhi ye baat bayan ki, to ham ne us se kaha : Hasan ke mutalliq ye na kahen . (yani is baat ki nisbat unki taraf na karen.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat hamarey nazdik batil hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) mazeed farmatey hain ke Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) guthli daar phal (khajoor aur kishmish waghera), pattey (janwaron ka chaaraa) aur (qabile-kaasht) beej zakhira rakhtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine Ahmed bin Yunus (Rahimahullah) se suna, unhoney kaha : maine Janab Sufiyan se birsim hijaazi (janwaron ke chaarey) ko dabaaney (rokney) ke mutalliq puchha , to unhoney kaha ke log ( Sahaba kiram ( zakhira andozi ko makruh samajhtey they. maine abu-Bakar bin Ayash se ye masla puchha to unhoney kaha ke zakhira kar saktey ho."
3449,Janab Alqama bin Abdullah apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon mein raaij sikke ko todney se mana farmaya hai siwaye iskey ke koi khas zarurat ho.
3450,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! narkh (bhaaw) muqarrar farma dijiye. aapney farmaya : ''(nahin) balke mein dua karunga (ke Allah taala qeematon me kami farma dey).'' phir eik aur aadmi aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! narkh muqarrar farma dijiye . aapney farmaya : ''(nahin) balke Allah hi ghataataa aur badhata hai, aur mujhey yaqeen hai ke main Allah se us haal mein miloonga ke kisi ko mujh par zulm ka dawa na hoga.''"
3451,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! narkh (bhaaw) bahut badh gaey hain, lihaza aap narkh muqarrar farma den. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Shan Wala Allah hi narkh muqarrar kerney wala hai, wohi tangi kerney wala, wusat deney wala, rozi rasaan (dene wala) hai. aur mujhey yaqeen hai ke main Allah se us haal mein miloonga ke tum mein se koi bhi mujh par kisi khoon ya maal ke maamley mein koi mutalba na rakhta hoga.''"
3452,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey jo ghalla bech raha tha. aapney us se puchha : kaisey bech rahey ho? usney bata diya. phir aap par wahi ki gaee ke apna haath is ghalley mein daliye. aapney apna haath is mein dala to usey geelaa paya . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo dhoka deta hai wo ham mein se nahin.''
3453,Yahya bayan kartey hain ke Janab Sufiyan (Rahimahullah) napasand kartey they ke (لیس منا [lais mana]) ki tafseer (لیس مثلنا[lais mislunaa]) se ki jaey.
3454,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khareedney aur bechney walon mein dono ko ikhtiyar hasil hota hai (ke wo apney saudey ko mansookh kar den) jab tak ke juda na ho jaeyn. siwaye iskey ke sauda hi ikhtiyar ka ho. (yani juda honey ke baad ki jitni ziyada ya kam muddat wo aapas mein tey kar len, ikhtiyar qaaim rahega.)"
3455,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. farmaya : ''ya koi doosrey ko yun keh dey ke) abhi ( pasand kar lo.''
3456,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do bikri karney walon ka juda honey se pehley tak ikhtiyar baqi rehta hai siwaey iske ke saudey mein ikhtiyar tey kar liya gaya ho, aur kisi ke liye bhi halal nahin ke sauda wapis kar liye janey ke andeshe ki wajeh se iraade ke saath apney sathi ko chhod kar chala jaey.''"
3457,"Janab Abul-Wazi se riwayat hai ke ham eik ghazwey mein gaey to ham ne eik manzil par padaaw kiya. hamarey eik sathi ne doosrey ko ghulam ke badley mein apna ghoda bechaa , phir wo dono baqi din aur raat ikhattey hi rahey. jab aglaa din hua aur koochh ka waqt aa gaya to ghodey ka kharidar apney ghodey ki taraf utha aur zeen rakh kar usey tayyar kerney laga to bechney waley ko apney saudey par nadaamat hui aur uskey paas aaya aur sauda mansookh kerney ki baat kerney laga , lekin ghoda leney waley ne wapis kerney se inkar kar diya. to usney kaha ke merey aur tumharey darmiyan (hukm) Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi hain. chunanche wo dono lashkar ki eik taraf Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur qissa bayan kiya. unhoney kaha : kya tum razi ho ke main tumharey darmiyan wo faisla kar dun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''do sauda kerney waley jab tak alehda alehda na ho jaeyn (sauda mansookh kerney ka ( unhen ikhtiyar rehta hai. Hisham bin Hassaan ne kaha ke Jameel (bin Murra) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main nahin samajhta ke tum juda juda huey ho."
3458,"Yahya bin Ayub bayan kartey hain ke Janab Abu-Zara'a (Rahimahullah) jab kisi se koi kharid aur farokht kartey to usko ikhtiyar detey , phir ussey kehtey ke mujhey ikhtiyar kar leney ki mohlat do. aur bayan kartey ke maine Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''(bai kerney waley ( dono afrad razamandi ke baghair hergiz juda na hun.''"
3459,"Hazrat Hakeem bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bai aur shara  kerney waley dono afrad ko juda honey se pehley tak ikhtiyar hasil rehta hai. agar wo sach bolen aur haqeeqat khol kar bayan keren to unki bai mein barkat hoti hai. aur agar wo haqeeqat chupaeyn aur jhoot bolen to unke saudey se barkat utha li jati hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Saeed bin Abi Aruba aur Hammad ne ( Qatada sey) aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. lekin Hammam ne ( Qatada sey) riwayat kartey huey kaha : ''yahan tak ke dono juda juda ho jaeyn ya ikhtiyar kerney ki shart kar lein.'' ye baat teen martaba farmaee."
3460,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi musalman ka sauda wapis kar liya,  Allah uski khataaen wapis kar lega.''  (yani maaf farma dega.)"
3461,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney eik saudey mein do saudey kiye to uskey liye un mein se ya to kam qeemat hai ya sood hai.''"
3462,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''jab tum eina ki bai kerney lago gey , bailon ki dumeen pakad lo gey , kheti baadi hi par mutmain ho jaogey aur jihad chhod baitho gey tu Allah tum par aisi zillat musallat kar dega jo kisi tarah zaayel (khatm) na hogi yahan tak ke tum apney deen ki taraf laut aao. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : ye hadees Jaafar (bin Musafir) ki hai aur lafz bhi usi ke hain."
3463,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to aapney unhen paya ke wo khajuron mein eik-eik , do-do aur teen-teen saal ke liye bai salaf kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi khajuron mein bai salaf karey to usey chahiye ke uska naap maloom ho, wazan maloom ho aur muddat bhi maloom ho.''"
3464,"Muhammad bin Mujaalid (ya Abdullah bin Mujaalid) ne bayan kiya ke Abdullah bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) ka bai salaf ke baarey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya to unhoney mujhey Hazrat ibne-Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja. chunanche maine un se sawal kiya, to unhoney kaha : bila-shuba ham log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein aur baad Azan Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat mein gehun, jau, khajoor aur kishmish ki bai bataur bai salaf kiya kartey they. ibne kaseer ne mazeed kaha : ham un logon se bai kartey they jinkey paas ye maal nahin hota tha. (Hafs bin umr aur ibne Kaseer) dono ne ittefaq se kaha : phir maine (yani Muhammad bin Mujaalid ya Abdullah bin Mujaalid ne) Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi se bhi puchha to unhoney isi tarah kaha ."
3465,"Yahya aur) Abdur-Rehman ( ibne Mehdi dono ba-waaste Shoba, Abdullah bin Abai Mujalid se riwayat kiya. jabkey Abdur-Rehman ne sirf ibne-Abi Mujalid kaha aur ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha : ham aisey logon se maamla kartey they ke ye chizen unke paas na hotin thin . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ''ibne-Abi Mujalid'' hi sahih hai aur is mein Shoba se khata hui hai."
3466,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abai Aufa Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Shaam ki taraf jihad ka safar kiya to wahan ke nabti log hamarey paas aatey aur phir ham un se bai salaf ki soorat mein gehun aur tel ka sauda, maloom-qeemat aur maloom-muddat ke sath kiya kartey they. inse kaha gaya : kya un logon se khareedtey they. jinkey paas ye chizen hoti thin? unhoney kaha : ham unse ye nahin puchha kartey they."
3467,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne doosrey se eik khajoor ke phal ki bai salam (salaf) kar li lekin us saal uspar koi phal na aaya to wo apna jhagda lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye . aapney (khajoor waley sey) farmaya : ''tum kyonkar uska maal halal samajhtey ho? uska maal usey wapis kar do.'' phir farmaya : ''khajoor (ya baagh) ki bai salaf mat karo yahan tak ke phal istimal ke qabil ho jaey.'' (khaas darkht ya khas baagh murad hai.)
3468,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi chiz mein bai salaf ki ho to usey dusri se na badley.''"
3469,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik shakhs ne phal khareedey jo aafat ka shikar ho gaey. so us par qarza bahut ziyada ho gaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey sadqa do.'' logon ne usko sadqa diya lekin wo uskey qarz ki adaegi ke liye pura na ho saka to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qarz khuwahon se farmaya : ''jo paatey ho ley lo, tumharey liye bas yehi hai.''"
3470,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to apney bhai ko khajoor bechey aur phir us mein aafat aa jaey to us se kuchh lena terey liye halal nahin, haq ke baghair apney bhai ka maal lena terey liye kyonkar munasib ho sakta hai?''"
3471,"Janab Ata (Rahimahullah) se manqul hai ke aafat se murad (wo) tamam zahiri asbab hain, maslan barish , zaalaa baari , tiddi dal , aandhi ya aag lagna waghaira (jo khet ya maal ko zaya kar den)."
3472,Janab Yahya bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke asal maal ki tihai se kam mein aafat aaye (aur nuqsan ho jaey) to uski talafi (bharpaee) zaroori nahin hai aur musalmanon mein aisey hi raaij hai.
3473,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghaas mehfooz rakhney ki gharz se zayed pani na roka jaey.''"
3474,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke aadmiyon se Shan Wala Allah qiyamat ke roz kalam nahin farmaeyga : eik wo aadmi jisney kisi musafir se apna baqiya pani rok liya ho. doosra wo jisney Asr ke baad kisi saudey par jhooti qasam khai ho aur teesra wo jisney Imam (aa'laa) se baiat ki ho, agar wo usey (duniya ka maal) deta rahey, to uska wafadar rahey aur agar na dey, to wafaa na karey."
3475,"Janab Aamash ne is riwayat ko apni sanad se usi hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya, kaha : ''aur Allah aisey logon ko paak nahin kerega aur unke liye dard naak azab hoga.'' aur farokht ke saman ke baarey mein kaha ke yun kahey : ''Allah ki qasam ! mujhey iska itna itna diya gaya (magar maine nahin diya lekin tumhen kam mein dey raha hun) aur doosra isko (iski is baat mein) sachcha samjhey aur usey kharid ley.''"
3476,Buhaisa naami eik khatoon apney walid se riwayat karti hai ke merey walid ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se milney ki ijazat li. phir wo aap ki qamis ke andar se ho kar aap ko chimat gaey aur aap ko choomney lagey. phir kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kis cheez ka rokna halal nahin? aapney farmaya : ''pani ka.'' phir kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kis cheez ka rokna halal nahin? aapney farmaya : ''namak ka.'' usney phir kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kis cheez ka rok lena halal nahin? aapney farmaya : ''bhalai kartey rehney mein tumharey liye khair hai.''
3477,"Muhajrin Sahaba mein se kisi se riwayat hai, usney kaha maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath teen baar jihad mein shirkat ki hai. maine aap ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''musalman teen chizon main eik doosrey ke shareek hain ghaas, pani aur aag.''"
3478,Hazrat Ayas bin Abd (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zayed pani ki farokht (bikri) se mana farmaya hai.
3479,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey aur billey ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai.
3480,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne billi ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai.
3481,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya ke aapney kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya ki kharchi aur kaahin (pujari) ke nazraney se mana farmaya hai."
3482,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai. aur agar wo (bechney wala) kuttey ki qeemat ka mutalba kerney aaye to uski hatheli mitti se bhar do.
3483,Janab Aun bin Abu-Juhaifa apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai.
3484,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kuttey ki qeemat , kaahin (pujari) ka nazrana aur zaaniya ki kharchi halal nahin.''"
3485,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beshak Allah taala ne sharab aur uski qeemat (yani kharid aur farokht) ko haram kiya hai, murdar aur uski qeemat ko haram kiya hai. khinzir aur uski qeemat ko haram kiya hai.''"
3486,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Fateh Makka ke saal jabkey aap Makka hi mein they, suna aap farma rahey they : ''beshak Allah taala ne sharab , murdar , khinzir aur buton ki kharid aur farokht haram thehrai hai.'' kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! murdar ki charbi ke mutalliq farmaeyn ke usey kashtiyon ke takhton aur chamdon par istimal kiya jata hai aur log isey chiraghon mein bhi jalaatey hain. aapney farmaya : ''nahin ye haram hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is moqe par farmaya : ''Allah taala yahudiyon ko halak karey, Allah taala ne jab un par is (murdar) ki charbi haram kar di to unhoney isey pighla kar bechnaa shuru kar diya aur phir iski qeemat khaney lagey.''"
3487,Yazid bin Abi Habib kehtey hain ke Ata ne Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye riwayat mujhey usi ki manind likh bheji magar is mein ([هو حرام]) ka lafz nahin tha.
3488,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (Baitullah mein) Hajre-Aswad ke paas baithey dekha . aapney apni nazar aasman ki taraf uthai aur hans diye . phir farmaya : ''Allah taala yahudiyon par lanat karey. . . . teen baar farmaya. . . . Allah taala ne un par charbiyon ka istimal haram kar diya to unhoney usey bechnaa shuru kar diya aur uski qeemat khaney lagey . bila-shuba Allah taala jab kisi qom par kisi chiz ka khana haram kar deta hai, to uski qeemat bhi haram kar deta hai. Khalid bin Abdullah Tahan ki riwayat mein ([رأيت]) ''maine dekha'' ka jumla nahin hai. aur) [ لعن الله اليهود ] ( ki bajaey ([قاتل الله اليهود]) kaha : yani ''Allah taala yahudiyon ko halak karey.''"
3489,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo sharab bechtaa hai usey chahiye ke khinzir ko (khana) halal samjhey.''"
3490,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jab Sura Baqara ki aakhiri aayaat nazil huin , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley aur unhen ham par padha aur farmaya : ''sharab ki tijarat haram kar di gaee hai.''"
3491,"Janab Aamash (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se is hadees ke ham-maani bayan kartey huey kaha ke aakhiri aayaat , jo sood se mutalliq hain (jab wo nazil huin)."
3492,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney koi ghalla (tuaam) (khana) kharida ho to usey apney qabzey mein liye baghair farokht na karey.''"
3493,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham ghalla kharida kartey they. isliye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas aadmi bhejtey jo hamen hukm deta ke ham usey farokht kerney se pehley kharidney ki jagah se dusri jagah muntaqil kar lein. yani andazey se (jo) kharid aur farokht kartey they (us se mana kar diya gaya).
3494,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke log mandi ki baalai (upri) janib andazey se ghalla khareedtey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko farokht kerney se mana farma diya, yahan tak ke wo usey dusri jagah muntaqil kar len."
3495,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke jisney mutayyan (tay-shuda) keel (naap) mein ghalla kharida ho, to usey qabzey mein liye baghair aagey farokht kar dey."
3496,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney ghalla kharida ho to usey farokht na karey yahan tak ke naap ley.'' (apney qabzey mein le-ley.) (raawi) Abu-Bakar ne mazeed kaha ke Taaus kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke aisa kyon hai? unhoney kaha : kya dekhtey nahin ho ke log usey soney ke badley kharid letey hain, halanke wo (ghalla) abhi bahut door hota hai. (farokht kerney waley ke paas pahuncha hi nahin hota.)"
3497,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi ghalla khareedey to jab tak usey apney qabzey mein na le-ley farokht na karey.'' Sulaiman bin Harab ke lafz they : ( [حتى يستوفيه] ( Musaddad ne izafa kiya ke Taaus ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : aur mera khayal hai ke her chiz tuaam (khane) (ghalle) ki tarah hai. (yani kharid hui cheez ko apney qabzey mein leney se pehley aagey farokht (bikri) nahin karna chahiye , chahey (chahe) uski nauiyat koi ho. ("
3498,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain : maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein agar koi ghalley ka dher khareedtaa aur phir wahin farokht kar deta to is par usey saza di jati thi , yahan tak ke apni manzil par ley jaey."
3499,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine baazar mein tel kharida. jab maine usey wasul kar liya to mujhey eik aadmi mila aur usney mujhey umda munaafe ki peshkash ki. maine chaha ke (usey qubul kartey huey) uskey haath par haath maarun. to eik shakhs ne merey peechey se mera bazu pakad liya. maine palat kar dekha to wo Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) they. unhoney kaha : jahan tum ne isey kharida hai usi jagah mat becho yahan tak ke apni manzil par ley jao. bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kharidney ki jagah hi par us maal ko bechney se mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke tajir isey apni-apni manzil par ley jaeyn.
3500,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha ke log kharid aur farokht mein mujhey dhoka dey jatey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''jab tum maamla karo to yun keh diya karo ke dhoka faraib nahin.'' chunanche wo sauda kartey huey kaha karta tha : ( [لا خلابة] ( ''dhoka faraib nahin.''"
3501,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik shakhs tha jo maamla kerney mein saada aur kamzor tha. uskey ghar waley Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! falan par pabandi laga dijiye . wo kharida aur farokht karta hai halanke wo maamla tey kerney mein bahut kamzor hai. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur kharid aur farokht se mana farmaya , to usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main is kaam se reh nahin sakta, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum kharid aur farokht nahin chhod saktey, to kaha karo : lao aur lo (maamla naqad karo) aur dhoka faraib nahin.'' Abu-Saur ne (أخبرنا سعيد) ki bajaey (عن سعيد) kaha ."
3502,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (بیع العربان) se mana farmaya hai. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : iski soorat jaisey ke ham samajhtey hain ye hai. . aur Allah behtar janta hai. . koi kisi se ghulam khareedey ya janwar kiraaye par ley, phir us se kahe ke main tujhey eik Dinar diye jata hun, agar maine ye sauda ya kiraaey par lena chhod diya (na liya) to jo maine tujhey diya ye tera hua. (warna asal qeemat mein shumar hoga.)"
3503,"Hazrat Hakeem bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain, maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! eik aadmi merey paas aata hai aur mujh se aisi chiz Khareedni chahta hai jo merey paas nahin hoti , to kya main uskey liye baazar se kharid laaun? aapney farmaya : ''jo terey paas nahin hai wo mat bech.''"
3504,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (bin Al-Aas) (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''udhaar aur bai aur eik bai mein do sharten halal nahin hain, aur us chiz ka nafa bhi halal nahin jo teri apni zamanat mein nahin aur jo chiz terey paas (yani qabzey mein) na ho usey mat farokht kar.''"
3505,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apna oont farokht kiya aur un se shart kar li ke main apney ghar tak is par sawari karunga. is hadees ke aakhir mein kaha : (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya ( : ''kya tum samajhtey ho ke maine tumhara nuqsan kiya hai taake main tumhara oont ley-lun? jao ! oont bhi ley jao aur uski qeemat bhi. dono hi tumharey hain.''
3506,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghulam ki bai aur uski salamti ki zamanat teen din tak hai.'' (tauzeeh nichey likhi hai.)"
3507,Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur mazeed kaha : agar teen (din) raat tak is mein kisi aeb key baarey mein pata chala to gawah pesh kiye baghair hi usey wapis kar sakega . aur agar teen din ke baad muttala hua to usey gawah pesh karna hoga ke jab usey kharida tha to us mein ye aeb tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke tauzeeh Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ka qaul hai.
3508,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aamdani ka haqdaar wohi hai jo zaamin ho.''
3509,"Janab Mukhlid bin Khafaaf Ghifaari (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke logon ke sath meri eik ghulam mein sharaakat thi , maine usey kaam par lagaya jabkey mera sathi ghayeb tha. to wo ghulam merey liye kama kar laya . merey shareek ne apney hissey ke baarey mein mujh se jhagda kiya aur muqadma qazi ke samney pesh kar diya. to qazi ne mujh se kaha ke main uska hissey ada kar dun. chunanche main Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber ke paas aaya aur waqia unhen bataya, to wo qazi ke paas gaey aur usey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki riwayat sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''aamdani ka wohi haqdaar hota hai jo zaamin ho.''"
3510,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) riwayat karti hain ke eik shakhs ne ghulam kharida, phir jab tak Allah ne chaha , wo uskey paas raha. baad iske usey ghulam ke kisi aeb ki khabar hui to wo uska maamla Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley gaya. aapney usey bechney waley ko wapis kara diya, to usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney merey ghulam se aamdani bhi li hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aamdani ka wohi haqdaar hota hai jo zaamin ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain iski sanad maiyaari nahin hai."
3511,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Qais bin Muhammad bin Ash-as apney walid ( Qais ( se aur wo Abdur-Rehman ke dada ( Muhammad ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Ash-as (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se bees hazar mein kuch ghulam khareedey jo ke khums ke they. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne qeemat leney ke liye aadmi bheja, to usney kaha ke maine unhen das hazar mein liya hai. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kisi aadmi ko muntakhab kar lo jo ham mein faisla kar dey. Hazrat Ash-as (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap khud hi merey aur apney darmiyan faisla kar den. to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''jab kharidar aur bechne waley ke darmiyan ikhtilaf ho jaey aur un mein koi gawah na ho, to baat farokht kerney waley ki moatabar hogi , ya wo dono hi soda chhod den.''"
3512,Janab Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman ne apney walid se riwayat kya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghulam bechey. aur alfaz mein kami beshi hai. mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya.
3513,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shufaa her mushtarak zameen ya baagh mein hai, usey apney shareek ko khabar diye baghair bechna durust nahin. agar (bina ittilaa) bech diya ho to wo shareek hi ziyada haqdaar hai yahan tak ke wo doosrey ke liye ijazat dey dey.''"
3514,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne her mushtarak ghair taqseem shuda chiz mein Shufaa rakha hai, lekin jab hudood mutayyan ho jaeyn aur raastey alag alag ho jaeyn to phir koi Shufaa nahin."
3515,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab zameen taqseem ho jaey aur hudood mutayyan ho jaeyn , to us mein koi Shufaa nahin .''"
3516,Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : '' hamsaaya apney qurb ki bina par ziyada haq daar hota hai.''
3517,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ghar ka hamsaaya , hamsaaey ke ghar ya zameen ka ziyada haqdaar hai.''"
3518,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamsaaya , hamsaaey par Shufaa ka ziyada haqdaar hai, agar wo mojud na ho to uska intizar kya jaey, b-sharte-ke unka raasta eik ho.''"
3519,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi kangaal aur muflis ho jaey aur phir koi ( maal deney wala ( apna maal uskey paas bilkul wesey hi paey , to doosron ki nisbat wohi uska ziyada haqdaar hai.''"
3520,"Janab abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney koi maal bechaa ho aur phir kharidar kangaal ho gaya ho aur bechney waley ne uski koi qeemat wasul na ki ho phir wo apney maal ko uskey paas bilkul wesey hi paey , to wohi uska ziyada haqdaar hoga , agar kharidar faut ho jaey to maal wala deegar qarz khuwahon ke sath barabar hoga .''"
3521,"Janab abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. . .) mazkura baala ( hadees Malik ( 3520 number (ke ham-maani riwayat kya. us mein mazeed kaha : ''agar uski kuch qeemat wasul kar li ho to phir wo us mein deegar qarz khuwahon ke barabar haq rakhta hoga. abu-Bakar ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya : ''jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur uskey paas kisi shakhs ka maal bilkul wesey hi mojud ho, usney usko koi qeemat bhi ada na ki ho to sahibe-maal doosrey qarz khuwahon jaisey sulook ka mustahiq hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Malik ki hadees ziyada sahih hai. (yani hadees : 3520 ( ."
3522,"Janab abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki manind bayan kya, kaha : ''agar uski qeemat se kuch wasul kar liya ho to baqi mein wo deegar qarz khuwahon ke barabar hoga. albatta agar koi shakhs halak ho jaey aur uskey paas kisi ka maal bilkul wesey hi mojud ho, wo chahe uski qeemat wasul kar chuka ho ya na , to wo baqi qarz khuwahon ke sath hoga .''"
3523,"Janab umr bin Khalda bayan kartey hain ke ham apney eik sahab ke silsiley mein , jo muflis ho gaya tha. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey unhoney farmaya : main her soorat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wala faisla karunga .) farmaya : ( jo shakhs muflis ya faut ho jaey aur maal wala bilkul wesey hi apna maal uskey paas paey , to wohi us maal ka ziyada haqdaar hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : kon is hadees ko qubul kerega .) raawi hadees ( Abul-Mo'atamir kon hai? yani ham usko nahin jantey ."
3524,"Janab Aamir Shobi (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jisey koi aisa janwer mila ho ke uskey Malik usko chaara deney se aajiz aagey hun aur phir unhoney usey chhod diya ho, to jo koi usey le-ley aur usey zinda kar ley to wo usi ka hua .) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ( Aban ki hadees mein farmatey hain : Ubaidullah (bin Humaid) kehtey hain : maine Janab Aamir se puchha ke ye kis se marwi (bayan) hai? to unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kaee eik Sahaba kiram se. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat Janab Hammad ki hai aur wazeh aur kamil hai."
3525,"Janab Shobi (Rahimahullah) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfooan bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi tabah haal janwer ko chhod diya ho aur koi doosra usey zinda kar ley (yani ilaj muaalija aur khidmat sey) to ye uska hua jisney usey zinda kya. ''"
3526,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' doodh waley janwer ka doodh nikala jaeyga jabkey usey rehan rakha gaya ho, us kharch ke iwaz jo us par hota hai. aur sawari waley janwer par sawari ki jaeygi jabkey usey rehan rakha gaya ho, us kharch ke iwaz jo us par hota hai. jo shakhs sawari karta hai aur doodh nikalta hai kharch bhi usi par hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees hamarey nazdik sahih hai."
3527,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke bandon mein kuch log aisey bhi hongey jo Nabi hongey na Shahid , magar qiyamat ke roz Allah ke yahan ( buland ( maraatib w manaazil ki wajeh se anbiya w shohda bhi un par rashk karengey .'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamen bataeyn , wo kon log hongey ? aapney farmaya : ''ye wo log hongey jo aapas mein Allah ki kitab (ya Allah ke sath mohabbat ( ki bina par mohabbat kartey they. halanke unka aapas mein koi rishta naataa ya maali lein deen na tha. Allah ki qasam ! unke chehrey Noor hongey aur wo log Noor par hongey . jab log khof-zada ho rahey hongey, to unhen koi khof na hoga. jab log ghamgin w pareshan ho rahey hongey, to unhen koi gham aur pareshani na hogi.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayate-karima tilawat farmaai : ألا إن أولياء الله لا خوف . ۔ ''aagah raho ! Allah ke waliyon ko na koi khof hoga, na wo gham khaeyngey.''"
3528,"Imaara bin Umair ki phuphi ne ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke eik yateem meri kafalat mein hai, kya main uskey maal mein se kha sakti hun? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''intehai pakizah maal jo insan khata hai wohi hai jo uski apni kamai ka ho, insan ki aulad uski apni kamai hi hai.''"
3529,"Imaara bin Umair apni walida sey, wo ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ki aulad uski apni kamai hai, balke behtareen kamai hai, chunanche tum unke maalon mein se kha saktey ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Hammad bin abi Suleman ne us riwayat mein ziyada kya hai. ( tum unki kamai kha saktey ho ( ''jab tum zarurat mand ho.'' magar ye izafa munkar ( zaeef ( hai."
3530,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas maal hai aur aulad bhi , aur mera walid merey maal ka zarurat mand rehta (yani leta rehta ( hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum aur tumhara maal tumharey walid ka hai. beshak tumhari auladen tumhari behtareen kamai hain, chunanche tum apni auladon ki kamai se kha saktey ho.''"
3531,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apna maal bilkul wesey hi kisi ke paas paey to wohi uska ziyada haq daar hai) lihaza wo le-ley (aur ( jiskey paas ye paya gaya hai) usey chahiye ke apney bechney waley ke dar pai ho (us par daawa karey. ("
3532,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Hind Umme-Muawiya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : beshak ( mera shohar ( abu-Sufiyaan bakheel aadmi hai aur mujhey utna nahin deta jo mujhey aur merey bachon ke liye kafi ho. agar main uskey maal mein se kuch ley lun , to kya mujhey koi gunah hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is qadr ley liya karo jo dastoor ke mutabiq tujhey aur terey bachon ke liye kafi ho.''"
3533,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Hind Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! beshak ( mera shohar ( abu-Sufiyaan bakheel aadmi hai. main agar uskey maal mein se uskey ayaal ( bachon ( par uski ijazat ke baghair kharch karun, to kya mujh par koi gunah hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dastoor ke mutabiq kharch karo, to tum par koi harj nahin .''"
3534,"Janab Yusuf bin Maahak makki ka bayan hai ke falan aadmi kaee yateemon ka sarparast tha aur main uska kharch likha karta tha. un yateemon ne usey eik hazar dirham ka mughaalta diya jo usney unko ada kar diya. phir maine ( kaatib ne ( unke maal mein do gunaa paya . maine us se kaha : wo hazar jo unhoney tujh se ( mughaalta de-kar ( liye hain nikal lo . us ( wali) ne kaha : nahin. mujhey merey walid ne bayan kya hai, usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna tha : jo tujhey ameen banaey, to uski amanat usey wapis kar dey aur jo teri khayanat karey, to uski khayanat na kar.''"
3535,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo tujhey ameen banaey, to uski amanat usey ada kar dey aur jo teri khayanat karey, to uski khayanat na kar .''"
3536,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hadiya qubul farmatey aur uska badal bhi diya kartey they.
3537,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam ! main aaj ke baad kisi ka hadiya qubul nahin karunga siwaye uskey ke koi Muhajir Quraishi ho ya Ansari ya dosi ya Saqafi ."
3538,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hadiya de-kar wapis ley leney wala aisey hai jaisey koi qai karey aur phir usey kha ley . Hammam (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ham to qai ko haram samajhtey hain."
3539,"Hazrat ibne-Umar aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi aadmi ko halal nahin ke koi Atiya dey ya hadiya aur phir usey wapis lota ley . siwaye baap ke jo wo apney bete ko dey (to wapis ley sakta hai) us shakhs ki misal jo Atiya de-kar wapis ley leta hai us kuttey ki si hai jo khata hai, jab pet bhar jaey to qai kar deta hai aur phir dobara usi ko khaney lag jata hai.''"
3540,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hadiya de-kar wapis leney waley ki misal kuttey ki si hai, jo qai karta aur phir dobara usey khaney lagta hai. to jab koi hiba kerney wala apna Atiya wapis leney lagey to usey bar-sare-aam khada kya jaey aur jo wapis ley raha ho uskey mutalliq puchha jaey phir wo chiz usey wapis de-di jaey.''"
3541,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney apney kisi bhai ki sifarish ki aur phir usey us par koi hadiya diya, to agar usney usey qubul kar liya to , wo sood ke darwazon mein se eik badey darwazey mein dakhil ho gaya .''"
3542,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid ne mujhey eik Atiya diya. Ismail bin Salim ne yun kaha : doosrey bachon ke muqabley mein mujhey apna eik ghulam Atiya kya. pas meri walida Umra binte-Rawaha ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jao aur unhen us atiye par gawah bana lo. chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur aap ko gawah bananey ke liye ye baat batai aur kaha ke maine apney bete Noman ko Atiya diya hai aur (meri ehliya ( Umra ne mujh se kaha hai ke main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us par gawah bana lun . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''kya terey uskey ilawa aur bhi bachey hain? ''kaha ke haan. farmaya : ''to kya to ne un sab ko uis tarah ka Atiya diya hai jo Noman ko diya hai? ''kaha : nahin. yahan baaz muhaddeseen ke lafz hain : ''ye zulm hai.'' aur baaz ne kaha : ''ye majboori aur lachari ka maamla hai. (khushi ka nahin warna to sabhi ko deta) us par merey ilawa kisi aur ko gawah bana ley.'' Mughira ki riwayat mein hai.'' kya tujhey pasand nahin ke terey sath khidmat aur ehsan kerney mein sab bachey barabar hon? ''kaha : haan. aapney farmaya : '' to is par merey ilawa kisi aur ko gawah bana ley.'' Majaalid ke alfaz hain : ''unka tujh par ye haq hai ke to un sab mein adl karey jaisey ke un sab par lazim hai ke teri khidmat karen. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : baaz raawiyon ne ( أكل بنيك ? ( kaha : aur baaz ne ( ولدك ( kaha . ibne-abi Khalid ne Shobi se riwayat kartey huey kaha : ''kya terey uskey ilawa bhi bete hain ?'' aur Abul-Zuha ne Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya (ألك ولد غيره).
3543,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid ne mujhey eik ghulam ata kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : ''ye ghulam kya aur kaisa hai? ''maine arz kya ke ye mera ghulam hai, merey walid ne mujhey diya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya usney terey sab bhaiyon ko usi tarah diya hai jaisey tujhey diya hai? ''maine arz kya : nahin. aapney farmaya : '' to usey wapis kar dey .''"
3544,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni aulad mein adl karo, apni aulad mein adl karo.''"
3545,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ne kaha : aap merey is bete ko apna ghulam hadiya kar den aur meri khatir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah bhi banaeyn . chunanche wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur kaha ke falan ki dukhtar (us ki apni biwi Umra binte-Rawaha ( ne mujh se mutalba kya hai ke main uskey bete ko eik ghulam dun aur Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah banaun . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya uskey aur bhai hain ?'' usney kaha : haan . aapney puchha : ''kya un sab ko bhi to ne is jaisa ( ghulam ( diya hai jaisa usko diya hai? '' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''ye durust nahin hai aur main sirf haq ka gawah banta hun.''
3546,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi shakhs kisi aurat ki ismat ka Malik bin jaey (yani aurat uskey nikah mein aa jaey ( to us aurat ko jayez nahin ke apney zati maal mein bhi tasarruf karey.''"
3547,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi aurat ko apney shohar ki ijazat ke baghair Atiya dena jayez nahin .''"
3548,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umra (Umar bhar ke liye diya gaya atiya) hamesha-hamesh ke liye uska ho jata hai jisko hiba kiya gaya.''"
3549,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki misl bayan kya hai.
3550,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''Umra usi ke liye baqi rahega jisko Atiya diya gaya ho.''
3551,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisey zindagi bhar ke liye koi Atiya diya gaya to ye uska aur uskey warison ka hua. us ( Atiya (ke waris wohi hongey jo uski aulad mein se uskey waris hongey .''"
3552,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke ham-maani bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Leis bin Saad ne Zohri ke wastey abu-Salma sey, unhoney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se usi tarah riwayat kya hai."
3553,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi ko aur uski aulad ko umr bhar ke liye Atiya diya gaya ho to ye usi ka hua jis ko diya gaya ho. ye deney waley ko wapis nahin loteyga, kyonkey usney aisa Atiya diya hai jis mein virasat chal nikli hai.''"
3554,Janab ibne-Shahab (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain jaisa ke us riwayat ko Aqeel aur Yazid bin abi Habib ne b-wasta ibne-Shahab usi tarah riwayat kya hai. albatta Auzaai ke alfaz mein ikhtilaf hai jo ke ibne-Shahab se naqal huey hain. aur Fuleh bin Suleman ne hadees Malik ki tarah riwayat kya hai.
3555,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : ''Umra jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( hamesha ke liye ( nafiz qarar diya hai wohi hai ke yun kahey : ''ye terey liye hai aur teri aulad ke liye hai.'' aur jab yun kahey : ''terey jeetey ji ye terey liye hai.'' to ye uskey Malik ko lot aaeyga.
3556,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ruqba ya umra ke andaz mein hadiya mat kya karo . jisey koi chiz bator ruqba ya umra di gaee ho to ye uskey warison ki ho gaee .'' (yani jisey di gaee ho.'' ("
3557,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik Ansari aurat ke baarey mein faisla farmaya jisey uskey bete ne khajuron ka eik baagh Atiya dey rakha tha aur wo faut ho gaee to bete ne kaha ke maine ye usey uski zindagi tak ke liye diya tha. us (denay waley) ke doosrey bhai bhi they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye zindagi mein uskey liye tha to maut ke baad bhi usi ka hai.'' bete ne kaha : maine ye usko sadqa diya tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir to ye tujh se aur bhi ziyada door hai.'' (ke sadqa de-kar wapis letey ho ! (
3558,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''umraa aur ruqba ke hadiye unke ehle ke ho jatey hain.'' (jinhen diye gaey hon. wapis nahin ho saktey.)"
3559,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney zindagi bhar ke liye koi hadiya kya ho to zindagi aur maut dono soorton mein uska hai jisko diya gaya hai. aur ruqba (ka hadiya) na kya karo. jisney koi chiz is andaz mein di ho to uska raasta wohi hai.'' (yani jisko de-di ho usi ki virasat mein jaeygi.)"
3560,"Janab Mujahid (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : umra ye hai ke eik insan doosrey se yun kahey : ''jab tak to zinda hai ye terey liye hai.'' pas jab yun keh diya to ye uski hui aur (uskey baad) uskey warison ki hai. aur ruqba ye hai ke insan doosrey se kahey: ''ye chiz ham mein se baad mein marney waley ke liye hai.'' ( agar to pehley mar gaya to meri hogi, warna teri rahi ( ."
3561,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haath ke zimmey hai jo usney liya yahan tak ke usey ada kar dey.'' phir Hasan (Basrii (Rahimahullah) ( bhool gaey aur kaha : aariyatan leney wala tumhara amanat daar hai us par koi zamanat nahin."
3562,"Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se ghazwa Hunain ke moqe par zirhen aariyatan talab kin to usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! kya zabardasti lena chahtey ho? aapney farmaya : '' nahin, balke aariyatan hain, ( agar zaya huin to ( ham unka iwaz dengey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Yazid (bin Harun ( ki ye riwayat Baghdad ki hai lekin Wasit mein jab ye riwayat bayan ki to alfaz us se mukhtalif they."
3563,"Abdullah bin Safwan ke khandan ke baaz afrad se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''aey Safwan ! kya terey paas aslaha hai? '' usney kaha : udhar ya zabardasti ke taur par ? aapney farmaya : '' nahin, balke udhar ke taur par .'' chunanche usney tees se chaalis ke darmiyan zirhen udhar din. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwa Hunain mein gaey . so jab mushrekin paspa ho gaey aur Safwan ki zirhen ikhatti ki gaeen to un mein se chand zirhen gum thin . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safwan se farmaya : '' ham teri zirhon mein se kuch gum paatey hain, to kya unka tawaan ada keren ?'' usney kaha : nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! aaj merey dil mein Islam ki wo raghbat hai jo us din na thi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : usney ye zirhen aariyatan Islam laney se pehley di thin magar uskey baad musalman ho gaya tha."
3564,aale-Safwan ke baaz logon se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zirhen aariyatan li thin . aur mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya.
3565,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne her haq waley ko uska haq dey diya hai to ab kisi waris ke liye wasiyat nahin, aur koi aurat apney ghar mein se apney shohar ki ijazat ke baghair koi chiz kharch na karey.'' kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! tuaam bhi nahin ? aapney farmaya : ''ye to hamarey afzal amwaal mein se hota hai.'' phir farmaya : '' maangey ki chiz wapis karna hogi . aur doodh ka janwer , jo Atiya diya gaya ho, lotaya jata hai. qarz ada karna lazim hai aur zaamin aadmi zimma ada kerega .''"
3566,"Janab Safwan bin Yaala apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''jab mera aadmi terey paas aaye to usey tees zirhen aur tees oont dey dena .'' to maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( ye udhar) zamaan hogi ya usey wapis ada karengey? farmaya : '' wapis ada karengey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke hibbaan , Hilal Raai ke mamu hain."
3567,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni eik ehliya ke ghar mein they ke Ummahaat momenin mein se kisi dusri ne khaadima ke haath (unki khidmat mein) eik piyala bheja jis mein khana tha. ghar wali ne apna haath maara aur piyala tod diya. ibne Musanna ne bayan kiya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tootey huey dono tukdey pakdey aur unhen eik doosrey ke sath milaayaa aur khana us mein dalney lagey aur farmatey jatey they : ''tumhari maa ko ghairat aa gaee hai.'' ibne Musanna ne izafa kiya. ''khao.'' chunanche sab ne khaya . yahan tak ke wo (ehliya) piyala lekar aa gaee jo uskey ghar mein tha. (ham Musaddad ki hadees ke alfaz ki taraf ruju kartey hain) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khao.'' aur aapney khaadima ko piyaley ke liye rokey rakha yahan tak ke wo khaney se farigh ho gaey . phir aapney sahih Salim piyala khaadima ke hawaley kiya aur tootaa hua ghar mein rakh liya."
3568,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine koi aurat nahin dekhi jo Safiya (Raziallahu anha) jaisa khana bananey wali ho. usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye khana tayyar kiya aur aap ki khidmat mein (merey ghar mein) bhej diya. mujhey us par taish aa gaya , to maine bartan tod diya. phir maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! iska kya kaffara hai jo maine kiya hai? aapney farmaya : '' bartan ke badley bartan aur khaney ke badley khana .''"
3569,"Janab Haram bin Mahisa apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ki oontni eik aadmi ke baagh mein dakhil ho gaee aur unki kheti kharab kar di, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya : ''kheti walon ke zimmey hai ke din ko us (kheti) ki hifazat keren aur janwaron ke malikon par lazim hai ke raat ko unki hifazat keren (baandh kar rakhen).''"
3570,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke meri eik oontni thi jo bahut nuqsan kiya karti thi. to wo eik baagh mein dakhil ho gaee aur wahan nuqsan kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein baat ki gaee to aapney faisla farmaya : ''din ke waqt baaghaat ki nigrani aur hifazat unke malikon ke zimmey hai aur raat ke waqt janwaron ki nigrani unke malikon ke zimmey hai aur raat ke waqt janwar jo nuqsan kar jaeyn , to wo unke malikon ke zimmey hai (ke usey pura keren).''"
